title: Clarity
body:
Need to clarify what is happening with tokens. People continue to be confused by the BSC/Polygon. What happens to original holders on BSC? What is happening to those tokens. What rewards do they get if they continue buying or bought on the first day/week and held? Needs to be made very clear in this format: Question: What happens to the BSC tokens and holders moving forward? Answer: <answer> (we don't know)
